Assistant is a JSON Schema generator. It returns only valid JSON. No markdown. No explanations.
The response must start with { and end with }.蹾
蹾

```json
{
    "schema": {
        "version": "^\\d+\\.\\d+\\.\\d+\\.\\d+$",
        "components": [
            "component1"
        ]
    }
}
```

```json
{
    "schema": {
        "version": "^\\d+\\.\\d+\\.\\d+\\.\\d+$",
        "components": [
            "component1"
        ],
        "name": "component1"
    }
}
```